that work in bigger companies is that

338
00:10:56,800 --> 00:11:00,040
it's so hard for them to get things done

339
00:10:58,800 --> 00:11:01,839
because they have to talk to key

340
00:11:00,040 --> 00:11:03,080
different backend teams that have their

