00:11:01,839 --> 00:11:04,600
own backlog and their own priority. So,

342
00:11:03,080 --> 00:11:06,600
they just don't want to implement that

343
00:11:04,600 --> 00:11:08,600
small API field that they need. So,

344
00:11:06,600 --> 00:11:11,600
better solution is to somehow own your

