00:11:08,600 --> 00:11:13,839
backend as a frontend team, as a client

346
00:11:11,600 --> 00:11:15,120
team. There's also a lot of complexity

347
00:11:13,839 --> 00:11:17,000
when you have to implement all these

348
00:11:15,120 --> 00:11:18,360
different APIs because they all look

349
00:11:17,000 --> 00:11:20,200
different, you need a different client

