370
00:11:57,960 --> 00:12:01,040
back-end for front-end, and back-end

371
00:11:59,640 --> 00:12:02,800
teams they develop pure back-end

372
00:12:01,040 --> 00:12:04,000
services. And this is very important for

373
00:12:02,800 --> 00:12:06,720
you as a front-end engineer because it

