00:12:25,040 --> 00:12:28,720
conditions and the most exciting work.

386
00:12:27,040 --> 00:12:30,720
So, even if you're in the front-end,

387
00:12:28,720 --> 00:12:33,280
make sure that you can also get things

388
00:12:30,720 --> 00:12:35,920
done in the back-end. Now, the advantage

389
00:12:33,280 --> 00:12:37,880
with BFFs is that you can adapt them to

