00:25:01,040 --> 00:25:04,440
it as a component into your design

764
00:25:02,680 --> 00:25:05,800
system. That might be a different repo.

765
00:25:04,440 --> 00:25:08,400
And you can do that with the coding

766
00:25:05,800 --> 00:25:10,200
agent in a single session if you have

767
00:25:08,400 --> 00:25:11,880
everything in a mono repo. If not, you

768
00:25:10,200 --> 00:25:13,800
have to somehow feed those two different

769
00:25:11,880 --> 00:25:16,520
repositories to your coding agent and

770
00:25:13,800 --> 00:25:18,600
everything becomes harder. So, combining

771
00:25:16,520 --> 00:25:20,440
micro frontends and microservices with a

772
00:25:18,600 --> 00:25:22,920
mono repo, it's usually the most

773
00:25:20,440 --> 00:25:24,720
efficient way to work with AI. Now, one

